available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getTransform\"><code>getTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInPath\"><code>isPointInPath()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInStroke\"><code>isPointInStroke()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/lineTo\"><code>lineTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/measureText\"><code>measureText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/moveTo\"><code>moveTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/putImageData\"><code>putImageData()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/quadraticCurveTo\"><code>quadraticCurveTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rect\"><code>rect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/resetTransform\"><code>resetTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/restore\"><code>restore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rotate\"><code>rotate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/save\"><code>save()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>scale()</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scrollPathIntoView\"><code>scrollPathIntoView()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setLineDash\"><code>setLineDash()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setTransform\"><code>setTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/stroke\"><code>stroke()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeRect\"><code>strokeRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/transform\"><code>transform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/translate\"><code>translate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die Methode <code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D</strong></code><strong><code>.scale()</code></strong> der Canvas 2D API skaliert das Canvas-Element um den Faktor x horizontal und um den Faktor y vertikal.</p>\n\n<p>Normalerweise ist eine Einheit auf dem Canvas genau ein Pixel. Wenn wir zum Beispiel einen Skalierungsfaktor von 0,5 Pixeln anwenden, ist eine Einheit 0,5 Pixel und alle Objekte werden mit der halben Größe gezeichnet. Analog dazu vergößert der Skalierungsfaktor 2,0 die Längeneinheit auf zwei Pixel. Die Objekte werden dann doppelt so groß gezeichnet.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">void <var><em>ctx</em>.scale(x, y);</var>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"x\"><code>x</code></dt>\n <dd>Skalierungsfaktor in horizontaler Richtung.</dd>\n <dt id=\"y\"><code>y</code></dt>\n <dd>Skalierungsfaktor in vertikaler Richtung</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"die_methode_scale_verwenden","title":"Die Methode <code>scale</code> verwenden","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Dies ist nur ein kurzes Beispiel, das die Methode <code>scale</code> benutzt.</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; highlight:[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fillRect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// reset current transformation matrix to the identity matrix</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setTransform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Editieren Sie den folgenden Code und sehen Sie die Änderungen sofort im Canvas:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scale/_sample_.playable_code.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"Die Methode scale verwenden"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"scale_verwenden_um_horizontal_oder_vertikal_zu_spiegeln","title":"<code>scale</code> verwenden, um horizontal oder vertikal zu spiegeln","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Sie können <code>ctx.scale(-1, 1)</code> benutzen, um den Inhalt horizontal zu spiegeln und <code>ctx.scale(1, -1)</code>, um ihn vertikal zu spiegeln.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code2 sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code2\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scale/_sample_.playable_code2.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"scale verwenden, um horizontal oder vertikal zu spiegeln"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-context-2d-scale\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CanvasRenderingContext2D.scale' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompabilität","title":"Browserkompabilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>E